{"tid":654823,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"原島大地算唔算混血之中比較令仔？ 🤔","createTime":"2018-05-06T03:30:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-06T06:16:44.000Z","uid":44730,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"efb6d89722f93566abe46991be3ffc90c99b9109","tid":654823,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T03:30:11.000Z","msg":"有冇睇佢最近同湯怡套新劇 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/14/105309_dc4d89861da876a3fb8154d45d96f0b1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F14%2F105309_dc4d89861da876a3fb8154d45d96f0b1.png&h=696d470f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1ec32872e9e0685ec520dd687da351a0413ef2ed","tid":654823,"uid":44730,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T03:33:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">電影《某年某月》原島大地長大了！第一次擔正做主角，你要知關於他的5件事</span><br />\n<br />\n原島大地，細細個就聽過呢個名？冇錯，十幾年前，佢出名係拍咗部《忘不了》，同當時得令嘅張柏芝做兩母子。時至今日，大地仔長大了，20歲出頭就擔正做《某年某月》男主角，仲同大佢10年嘅「姐姐」湯怡一齊「談戀愛」，雖然年齡有啲距離，但毫無違和感<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.cosmopolitan.com.hk/var/cosmopolitanhk/storage/images/love/daichi-harashima-film-actor/2042442-1-chi-HK/5_img_750_h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cosmopolitan.com.hk%2Fvar%2Fcosmopolitanhk%2Fstorage%2Fimages%2Flove%2Fdaichi-harashima-film-actor%2F2042442-1-chi-HK%2F5_img_750_h.jpg&h=683ce470&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"581ccfc94c6a767d73aadb1703f604c45b1ce91e","tid":654823,"uid":70988,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T03:36:23.000Z","msg":"冇，7"},{"pid":"797a65432faeb4caabc90643042d02e8c8d92f1e","tid":654823,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T03:42:49.000Z","msg":"中日混血兒，97年出生，3歲參加了日本藝術團體選新秀的節目，勝出之後正式入行。拍過電影《母親快樂》、《超班寶寶》，因《忘不了》而為人認識。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://imgs.nmplus.hk/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/079927c73ece1d9041d255f97a928066.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgs.nmplus.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F04%2F079927c73ece1d9041d255f97a928066.jpg&h=c3fc9d58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://imgs.nmplus.hk/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/200403250368_607182.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgs.nmplus.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F04%2F200403250368_607182.jpg&h=548fecd4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大地由02年就開始拍戲，喺香港同內地拍過嘅電影有10幾部，不過最令人印象深刻，一定係睇過就喊過嘅《忘不了》，尤其張栢芝拖住飾演樂樂嘅大地去保良局，大地喊晒口叫栢芝唔好唔要佢嗰一幕"},{"pid":"c54468a29d7726b804a3bb0268fc2f2779f7a50f","tid":654823,"uid":55279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T03:44:17.000Z","msg":"麻麻哋 可能再老啲先"},{"pid":"f4e7dfcb9e9688a838f61bb6cbecf40ce87f9735","tid":654823,"uid":44730,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T03:45:41.000Z","msg":"家庭背景睇落複雜，但其實唔算。中地喺東京出世，但因為又中又日，所以佢細細個就講到聽到廣東話、日文、普通話呢三種語言。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.cosmopolitan.com.hk/var/cosmopolitanhk/storage/images/love/yddd/1/2042475-1-chi-HK/1_img_750_h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cosmopolitan.com.hk%2Fvar%2Fcosmopolitanhk%2Fstorage%2Fimages%2Flove%2Fyddd%2F1%2F2042475-1-chi-HK%2F1_img_750_h.jpg&h=376e146a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7354a1a0110d58c90163512d1003101aa781a6b8","tid":654823,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T04:03:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇，7</blockquote><br />\n邊度7🤔"},{"pid":"e38c12fbc9f92f00a3472056c43cb7f43e1a6cd7","tid":654823,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T04:03:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>麻麻哋 可能再老啲先</blockquote><br />\n愈老愈型？🤔"},{"pid":"c5a818b8c561c4e3dec2777798f6db8d958cf8ed","tid":654823,"uid":70988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7354a1a0110d58c90163512d1003101aa781a6b8","tid":654823,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T04:03:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇，7</blockquote><br />\n邊度7🤔"},"cite